  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2022-05-27",
    "date": "2022-06-21T17:46:26Z",
    "text": "Support Ukraine Through Our Tax Code Act\n\nThis bill denies the foreign tax credit and the tax deduction for income, war profits, and excess profits taxes paid to Russia and Belarus.\n\nThe bill also denies certain other tax benefits in connection with the invasion of Ukraine, including any tax treaty benefits and exemptions from withholding requirements.\n\nThe bill suspends tax information exchanges for Russia and Belarus under a tax treaty or an intergovernmental agreement during the period of the Ukraine invasion."
  },
